    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.47.8a" />
                
                <opener>
                <dateline>
                Skyrim, Sep. 25, '65
                </dateline>
                    
                <salute>Dear Slade:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>Please send a set of your three articles to my publisher.
                
                <address>
                    <addrLine>Mr. Bruce Nicoll, Dir.,</addrLine>
                    <addrLine>The University of Neb Press,</addrLine>
                    <addrLine>Lincoln, Neb.</addrLine>
                </address>
                
                I'm sure he will appreciate the kindness</p>
              
              <closer>  
                <salute>Affectionately</salute>
                <signed>John N.</signed>
              </closer>
                
                    <postscript>
                <p>I'm off <del><unclear>on</unclear></del> for the lecture tour!</p>
                    
                
                <note type="authorial">(see back)</note>
                
                <note type="authorial"><del>See <hi rend="underline">inside</hi></del></note>
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.47.8b"/>
                <fw type="curatorial"><del/></fw>
                
                <p>It would be bully if you cared to draft a note to Nicoll, <del>saying</del> telling of the 4th article on the <hi rend="underline">Prayer Garden</hi>. You could let him know your connection with Cornell.</p>
                <closer>
                &#8212; <signed>John</signed>
                </closer>
                    </postscript>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">8</fw>
                
            </div1>
        </body>
        
